{
  "stem": "6777.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I got with a bread cart and went back to my people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no-- well, way before the uprising.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, when we lost the flat where the bandits came, we went for some time into a safe house where my friends, the resistance people, lived.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I felt it wasn't safe there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Though we provide-- they provided for me in a village, real village, not any more little town or anything, a summer house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because well-to-do people have been still going for the summer months out of the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went from their place into this place in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day I came back, because I had to come back to be in contact with the resistance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they've been taken away from two places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three people, [INAUDIBLE], [INAUDIBLE], and Vodak, have been from one place, where we stayed just before going to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from another address in Warsaw, another two men-- they all were taken away by the Gestapo on the one day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I've met him in Kalisz after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the others have never been seen again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I asked him, when you've been arrested, when you've been taken away, what did they accuse you of, of hiding Jews?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, no, there has never been any question.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We've been taken to the Gestapo and a bit questioned, tortured, but not one question was about us helping or hiding any Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was all only about the resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we never gave any other names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We've been real friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this boy-- young man, I would say-- he got finished in Bergen-Belsen and was freed by the Russians, I think.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or was it American?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
